    • uiReadyAdditionalTripSegment

      public static AddnlTripSegmentBuilder uiReadyAdditionalTripSegment()
      Creates a ui ready trip segment builder with the following field set:
      • TripSegment - if this builder is used via the withAddnlTripSegment() method of a trip segment builder, then use the segment created by the builder. Otherwise create a new ui ready trip segment.
      • TransportType - set to one of the valid transport types
      Returns:
      a new trip segment builder
